What we'll focus on now is how
to search for jobs effectively

4
00:00:09,289 --> 00:00:13,399
to reduce the amount of stress and time
you'll spend on each job application.

5
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:17,230
While you're searching for jobs, you
should know what you want, research to

6
