Knowing what you want and only searching
for roles that match these requirements

8
00:00:25,429 --> 00:00:28,100
makes it easier for
you to find the right jobs for you.

9
00:00:28,100 --> 00:00:30,230
It eliminates a lot of
job search fatigue, so

10
