11
00:00:33,770 --> 00:00:36,120
Before you begin a job search,
write down two or

12
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:38,179
three things you cannot compromise on.

13
00:00:38,179 --> 00:00:41,659
For example,
your requirements may be location.

14
00:00:41,659 --> 00:00:42,969
You and
your family may not be able to move.

15
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:45,820
Another is company mission.

16
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:48,119
You want to do work you're proud of.

17
00:00:48,119 --> 00:00:49,719
Another important one is the role.

18
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:53,640
This may seem obvious, but making
a distinction between the jobs you could

