job, even if its in a location you
don't want to live in, even if its for

22
00:01:05,010 --> 00:01:07,550
a company whose mission
you're not passionate about.

23
00:01:07,549 --> 00:01:11,539
Although being open to anything may seem
like a good thing, to the employer it

24
